<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PayNow Instructions</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: rgb(220, 220, 215);
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: rgb(28, 57, 152);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .login-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .main-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .option-button {
            background-color: rgb(28, 57, 152);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: fit-content;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            grid-column: 1;
            align-self: start;
        }

        .qr-code {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            grid-row: 2;
        }

        .qr-image {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
        }

        .instructions {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .step {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#">Product</a>
            <a href="#">Cart</a>
            <a href="#">Payment</a>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="login-link">Login</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-container">
        <button class="option-button">Option 3</button>
        
        <div class="qr-code">
            <img src="qr.png" alt="PayNow QR Code" class="qr-image">
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
            <div class="step">1)Save the QR code.</div>
            <div class="step">2)Upload the QR code in any PayNow supporting app to make payment. Ensure that recipient is Chip Company.</div>
            <div class="step">3)You will receive a notification after payment is received by company. The transaction should be reflected in wallet transaction history.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>